-- Two Men Arrested on Board Plane at Stansted, U.K. Police Say
-- B y   T h o m a s   P e n n y
-- 2013-05-24T13:57:56Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-05-24/two-men-arrested-on-board-plane-at-stansted-u-k-police-say.html
Two men have been arrested on board a
passenger plane after it was diverted to Stansted Airport
outside  London  by two Royal Air Force fighter jets, police said.  “Essex Police has boarded a passenger plane diverted to
Stansted Airport and two men have been arrested on suspicion of
endangerment of an aircraft,” the force said in a statement
posted on its website. “ They have been removed from the
plane.”  RAF jets intercepted the Pakistan International Airlines
flight on its way to Manchester in northern  England .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Thomas Penny in London at 
